# LiveKit Plugins Clova

Agent Framework plugin for speech-to-text with Clova's API. Currently supports speech-to-text.

## Installation

```bash
pip install livekit-plugins-clova
```

## Pre-requisites

You need invoke url and secret key from Naver cloud platform -> Clova Speech and set as environment variables. Requires `CLOVA_STT_INVOKE_URL` and `CLOVA_STT_SECRET_KEY`
